title: Sigma Nu Quarter Zip Pullover Sweatshirt
features: Monogrammed with Sigma Nu and Sig Nu Letters
description: Our Sigma Nu quarter zip pullover is just perfect for this time of year. This pullover sweatshirt comes in dark heather grey and embroidered in white thread and sized S - 3XL. Our attention to detail and quality of embroidery sets us apart. All of our embroidered gifts are ready to leave our shop in California within 2-3 business days. Sweatshirt comes with Sig Nu Greek letters and Sigma Nu embroidered below the letters. 1 x 1 rib cuffs and waistband.
